data.title: Liberty Classic Community Band Festival XIII
data.meta_description: If you love concert band music, the Repasz Band once again hosts the 13th annual Liberty Classic Community Band Festival ...
data.text: If you love concert band music, the Repasz Band once again hosts the 13th annual Liberty Classic Community Band Festival with a free public concert Sunday, October 20th at 1:30 pm at the Community Arts Center in Williamsport. Under the baton of internationally known and respected veteran band-master, Colonel Arnald D. Gabriel, USAF Band (retired), this festival is a gathering and celebration of some of the world’s best concert band music, by committed life-long musicians from across the country and directed by one of the world’s truly outstanding and legendary bandmasters!
